app deploy - Deploy the app

Deploys the application to the given target.

Usage:
  app deploy [options] <target> [<files>...]

Options:
  -f, --force            Skip confirmation
  --[no-]dry-run         Print plan without executing (default: true)
  -r, --region <region>  Target region (default: us-east)

Global Options:
  -v, --verbose          Verbose output
  -c, --config <config>  Config file

Arguments:
  <target>      Deploy target name
  [<files>...]  Files to upload alongside the deploy
